----------------------------------------------------------------------------
                   Somewhere (over the Rainbow) - Jimi Hendrix
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Album: Crash Landing (1975)
Tabbed by: Alex Schwer
Email: schwer039@yahoo.com
Tuning: down 1/2 step


 /  slide up
 \  slide down
 h  hammer-on
 p  pull-off
 ~  vibrato
 +  harmonic
 x  Mute note
 sb  slight bend
 b   bend
 rb  release bend
 () tough to hear

Intro:

